# 🎯 QuizRank

QuizRank is a frontend-based online quiz application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can register, log in, take quizzes, view their scores, and check the leaderboard rankings.

## Features

* User Registration
* User Login
* Quiz Interface
* Multiple Choice Questions
* Question Navigation
* Timer Functionality
* Score Calculation
* Results Page
* Leaderboard
* Retry Quiz
* Logout Option
* Responsive Design

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* Local Storage

## Project Structure


